videos.description: Dillon Gabriel airs it out to Gabriel Davis as Davis leaps in the end zone to bring down a 19-yard touchdown.

videos.description: On fourth down, South Florida QB Jordan McCloud gets picked off by UCF's Antwan Collier, who returns the ball for 20 yards.

videos.description: Adrian Killins Jr. gets the ball and speeds away from the South Florida defense for a 35-yard score to extend UCF's lead to 14-0.

videos.headline: Killins bursts through hole for 35-yard UCF TD

videos.description: Dillon Gabriel finds Gabriel Davis wide open downfield for a 32-yard touchdown, their second scoring play of the game.

videos.headline: Gabriel, Davis connect again for 32-yard TD
